{"word":"H2891 - טהר - ṭâhêr - taw-hare'","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: טהר"},{"paragraph":"Transliteration: ṭâhêr"},{"paragraph":"Phonetic: taw-hare'"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுத்தமாக, சுத்தமாயிரு, சுத்திகரி, சுத்தம்பண்ணு, சுத்திகரிக்கப்படு, நீங்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be clean, be pure"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to be clean (physically, used of disease)"},{"paragraph":"2) to be clean ceremonially"},{"paragraph":"3) to purify, to be clean morally, to made clean"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to cleanse, purify"},{"paragraph":"a) physically"},{"paragraph":"b) ceremonially"},{"paragraph":"c) morally"},{"paragraph":"2) to pronounce clean"},{"paragraph":"3) to perform the ceremony of cleansing"},{"paragraph":"c) (Pual) to be cleansed, be pronounced clean"},{"paragraph":"d) (Hithpael)"},{"paragraph":"1) to purify oneself"},{"paragraph":"a) ceremonially"},{"paragraph":"b) morally"},{"paragraph":"2) to present oneself for purification"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Cognate: <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H2889 - טהר טהור - ṭâhôr ṭâhôr - taw-hore'/2889\">H2889</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H2890 - טהור - ṭehôr - teh-hore'/2890\">H2890</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H2891 - טהר - ṭâhêr - taw-hare'/2891\">H2891</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H2892 - טהר - ṭôhar - to'-har/2892\">H2892</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H2893 - טהרה - ṭohŏrâh - toh-or-aw'/2893\">H2893</a>"}]}